item.title: Release Notes
item.description: Version 1.11.0 (not yet released) Version 1.10.0 (2018-08-12) Change: HtmlUnit updated to the latest release 2.32 (HtmlUnit Release Notes). This implies changed FF support; we are now supporting FF60 and FF52. Change: Reworked table handling (used by the table filter [col; row]. This will many problem with tables using rowspan and colspan. Change: Reworked parts of the ByLabelMatcher to get better results. Change: Minor layout change for the output.
